              <p>By accessing our websites(hypebolt.ink & hypebolt.ca), submitting a pitch, viewing our films, or otherwise using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.</p>

              <h2>1. Film Production Services</h2>
              <p>HypeBolt Studios primarily focuses on the creation and production of its own films, akin to major film studios. Our services encompass various stages of filmmaking, including development, pre-production, production, and post-production.</p>

              <h2>2. Third-Party Pitch Submissions</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>We accept film pitches from third-party individuals through our online pitch form available on our website.</li>
                <li>Submitters must be at least 16 years of age in Canada, 18 years of age in the United States, and meet the minimum working age in their respective countries. By submitting a pitch, you confirm that you meet these age requirements.</li>
                <li>By submitting a pitch, you retain the copyright to your original intellectual property, such as characters and core concepts.</li>
                <li>However, by submitting a pitch, you grant HypeBolt Studios the right to review and consider your submission for potential development into a film adaptation.</li>
                <li>If HypeBolt Studios elects to move forward with a project based on your pitch, a separate agreement will be established to address the transfer or licensing of film rights. HypeBolt Studios will own the film rights, soundtrack, animation (if any), and all other assets created by our studio's crew.</li>
                <li>If HypeBolt Studios decides not to pursue a project based on your pitch, the rights to your original intellectual property remain with you.</li>
              </ul>

              <h2>3. Use of Our Films</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>Our films are intended for personal, non-commercial viewing only.</li>
                <li>You are strictly prohibited from uploading our films in their entirety to the internet or any other platform.</li>
                <li>Sharing clips from our films is permitted, provided that clear and visible credit is given to HypeBolt Studios.</li>
                <li>Unauthorized reproduction, distribution, public performance, or broadcasting of our films is prohibited.</li>
                <li>You may not alter, edit, or create derivative works from our films without our explicit written permission, except where such modifications constitute fair use, such as in the creation of YouTube Poop (YTP) content, provided the resulting work is significantly transformed and does not closely resemble the original film.</li>
                <li>Our films are provided "as is" without any warranties, express or implied.</li>
                <li>HypeBolt Studios shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages arising out of or in any way connected with the viewing or use of our films.</li>
                <li>All rights, including copyright, in and to our films are owned by HypeBolt Studios.</li>
                <li>HypeBolt Studios and its logo are trademarks of HypeBolt Studios. Their unauthorized use is prohibited.</li>
              </ul>

              <h2>4. Use of HypeBolt Studios Branding</h2>
              <p>You are permitted to use HypeBolt Studios branding, including our name and logo, in any form, including within your own films or content, provided that clear credit is given to HypeBolt Studios as the owner of the branding.</p>

              <h2>5. Data Collection and Privacy</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>We collect your IP address to enable your connection to our website, as is standard practice for all websites.</li>
                <li>If you submit a pitch through our online form, we collect your Name, Email address, and the details of your film pitch.</li>
                <li>Our practices regarding the collection, use, and protection of your personal data are outlined in our Privacy Policy, which you should review separately.</li>
              </ul>

              <h2>6. Communication Regarding Pitches</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>All official communication from HypeBolt Studios regarding submitted pitches will be conducted via email addresses with the domains @hypebolt.ink and @hypebolt.ca.</li>
                <li>Any emails received from addresses outside of these domains should be disregarded as potentially fraudulent.</li>
              </ul>

              <h2>7. Governing Law</h2>
              <p>These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Province of British Columbia, Canada.</p>
